*tlohi          (tlo, thi; real, free format)
   1.0E-01   1.0E+04
*nlohi          (nlo, nhi; real, free format)
   1.0E+14   1.0E+22
*numnuc         (nnuc; integer, free format)
   1
*nucspec        (nz, izlo, izhi; integers, one triplet per line)
    1  0  1
*flag           ('adpak', 'strahl', 'adas' or 'amns', free format)
  'adas'
*tailep         (real, free format)
   0.08
'b2ardr_rtnt'             '100'     # Use finer discretization for AFN (default 40)
'b2ardr_rtnn'             '100'     # Use finer discretization for AFN (default 32)
'b2ardr_no_weisheit'      '1'       # No correction for hydrogen neutrals
'b2ardr_amjhydhel'        '1'       # Take AMJUEL/HYDHEL for hydrogen neutrals
'b2ardr_t_min'            '1.0E-01' # Minimum temperature [eV] for which AMJUEL rates are evaluated
'b2ardr_nn_min'           '1.0E+14' # Minimum density [m^-3] for which AMJUEL rates are evaluated
'b2ardr_fix_recomb'       '1'
'b2ardr_nreac'            '2'       # Number of reactions explicitly specified below *nreac
*reac
AMJUEL H.4  2.1.5 EI
AMJUEL H.10 2.1.5 EI
